<del rend="strikethrough">aufgehalten </del> genomen hat / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns ~ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_222_r1l8">wol geſagt vnd cʒu vviſſen getan / vvie Jr euch vaſt vnd ſere <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>ern</ex></expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
